<T>__{inside the room:}
<A>__{nothing can stop the women and children from fleeing into the bedrooms. paul is frozen at the crash of rifles on the door. the door gives, soldiers flood in. they are startled by the crowd in the living room, rifles raised,}
<B>__{shouts.}
<C>__{soldiers}
<D>__{out, get out now!}
<A>__{paul pulls himself together, marches over to the soldier.}
<C>__{paul}
